Ivy Ross at Business Innovation Factory “Enabling innovation”
Ivy Ross: Does your organization have an innovation vibe?
Ambidextrous, Stanford Design School Magazine 2006[31]
Project Platypus: Reinventing Product Development at Mattel, An Interview with Ivy Ross, AIGA March 6, 2003

